sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Customer
    participant V_API as Vercel API (/api/online-order)
    participant DB as Supabase (order_queue)
    participant V_Worker as Vercel Cron (/api/queue-worker)
    participant G as Google Apps Script
    participant S as Google Sheets

    C->>+V_API: POST /api/online-order (placeOrder)
    V_API->>+DB: INSERT into order_queue (status: PENDING)
    DB-->>-V_API: { ok: true }
    V_API-->>-C: { ok: true, orderRef }

    Note right of V_API: Enqueues order immediately.\nFast, reliable response to customer.

    V_Worker->>+DB: 1. Claim PENDING orders (atomic UPDATE)
    DB-->>-V_Worker: ordersToProcess[]

    loop For each order
        V_Worker->>+G: 2. fetch(GAS_URL)
        G->>+S: appendRow(orderData)
        S-->>-G: Success
        G-->>-V_Worker: { success: true }
        V_Worker->>+DB: 3. UPDATE order_queue (status: COMPLETED)
        DB-->>-V_Worker: { ok: true }
    end

    Note over V_Worker,S: Worker processes queue sequentially,\neliminating GAS concurrency errors.\nIncludes retry and dead-letter logic.
